text.paragraph:
Carisoprodol, the active ingredient in carisoprodol tablets USP, has been subject to abuse, dependence, withdrawal, misuse, and criminal diversion [see Drug Abuse and Dependence (9.1, 9.2, 9.3)
                           ]. Abuse of carisoprodol poses a risk of overdosage which may lead to death, CNS and respiratory depression, hypotension, seizures, and other disorders [see Overdosage (10)
                           ].
